title: Yet Another Zombie Defense HD
description: Yet Another Zombie Defense HD is all about defending yourself against hordes of darkness attacking you every night. However, when you're the only survivor struggling against waves of enemies who are getting stronger and stronger, your end is inevitable. The only important question is how long can YOU survive?The game is a top-down arcade zombie shooter with strategy elements.
